{"id":161,"date":"2020-08-02T17:43:02","date_gmt":"2020-08-02T17:43:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes\/?page_id=161"},"modified":"2021-06-28T08:57:40","modified_gmt":"2021-06-28T08:57:40","slug":"fundraise","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/get-involved\/fundraise\/","title":{"rendered":"Fundraise"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2>Fundraise for KHT<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>At KHT we love being a little creative, so whether you are into your running, cooking, music or jumping out of planes, there are many different ways to fundraise to support us!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By fundraising for us, you make vital contributions to building sustainable futures for Karen communities across Northern Thailand whilst ensuring that we can carry on the amazing work that we do. As a small charity, we aim to use all the money raised by you to improve the lives of the Karen people in Thailand. Continue reading to find out how you could fundraise for KHT!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\" id=\"fundraising-ideas\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\">How can you Fundraise for KHT?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<section id=\"page-section-block_5f58b33b56bdf\" \nclass=\"page-section page-section--transparent\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-section__wrapper page-section--align-right\">\n            <div class=\"page-section__image\" style=\"max-height:400px\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2014-03-02-09.27.58.jpg\" alt=\"Sponsored Events\" \/>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"page-section__content\">\n                <h2 class=\"page-section__title\">Sponsored Events<\/h2>\n                                <p class=\"page-section__body \"><p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Over the years, our volunteers have taken part in a whole host of sponsored events. These kind of events allow you raise vital funds for KHT whilst trying something a little bit out of the ordinary!<\/p>\n<p>Why not take part in a sponsored event or create your own. In the past we have had people run marathons, skydive, bungee jump and even cycle all the way to Turkey! Sponsored events are a great way to raise money for KHT.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Get in touch using our contact us page if you are thinking about doing a sponsored event for KHT and we will be able to help you out every step of the way!<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<\/p>                                    <a href=\"\/about-us\/contact-us\/\" class=\"page-section__cta\">Contact Us!<\/a>                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section id=\"page-section-block_5f58b3a856be0\" \nclass=\"page-section page-section--cream\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-section__wrapper \">\n            <div class=\"page-section__image\" style=\"max-height:400px\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/L1190593.jpg\" alt=\"Jungle Trek\" \/>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"page-section__content\">\n                <h2 class=\"page-section__title\">Jungle Trek<\/h2>\n                                <p class=\"page-section__body \"><p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>KHT also hosts its own sponsored event in the form of an annual fundraising trek through the forests of Northern Thailand.<\/p>\n<p>Over five days, covering an average distance of 12 kilometres per day, the trek provides a unique chance to visit our past and present projects and glimpse into the Karen world as you sleep in the depths of the forest and within remote Karen villages. We aim to run our jungle trek every year, however, please be warned, places are limited and fill up fast!<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>You can find out more about what the trek entails by reading our latest blog post on our most recent trek!<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<\/p>                                    <a href=\"\/about-us\/news\/\" class=\"page-section__cta\">Trek Blog Post!<\/a>                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section id=\"page-section-block_5f58b4f756be1\" \nclass=\"page-section page-section--transparent\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-section__wrapper page-section--align-right\">\n            <div class=\"page-section__image\" style=\"max-height:400px\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/IMG_0882.jpg\" alt=\"Other Ideas!\" \/>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"page-section__content\">\n                <h2 class=\"page-section__title\">Other Ideas!<\/h2>\n                                <p class=\"page-section__body \"><p>There are loads of other ways you can get creative to fundraise for KHT. Why not get your workplace, school or local community group involved and organise a bake sale. If you are feeling musical, you could dust off that guitar or tune those vocal cords and do some busking.<\/p>\n<p>Hold a coffee morning to not only raise valuable funds but to also to raise awareness of the work KHT is doing. Host a Thai themed dinner party or curry night in aid of KHT, for some inspiration take a look at some of our very own Thai recipes. Shake it up and volunteer to take one of our collecting tins out onto the streets or into your workplace.<\/p>\n<p>The opportunities are endless! Make sure to get in contact with us before you host anything, as we might be able to provide you with vital information and resources to make your event extra special!<\/p>\n<\/p>                                    <a href=\"\/support-us\/donate\/\" class=\"page-section__cta\">Donate Now!<\/a>                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n<aside class